---
title: Penne with Beef & Zucchini Ragù plus Parmesan Cheese
description: Trying to get in more veggies at dinner? We’ve got just the thing! You’ll grate zucchini and swirl the shreds into an Italian-seasoned tomato sauce. The mild veg merges into the beefy sauce without changing the flavor—the perfect way to sneak in some green! The creamy ragù is tossed with penne and sprinkled with Parmesan for a delicious quick-to-the-table dinner.
